Which of the following commands displays CPU- related performance information a total of10 times gathered every 2 seconds?
A)  sar - u 2 10
B)  sar - u 10 2
C)  sar - u 2
D)  uptime - t
A
A. The sar command can be used for this purpose and, when provided with numbers in theformat displayed, will update every X seconds for Y executions.
